---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer
  class="bg-gray-950 text-white flex flex-col py-4 px-4 w-full border-t border-gray-700 rounded-t-lg mt-16"
>
  <div
    class="w-full max-w-screen-xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center text-center md:text-left"
  >
    <p class="text-sm mb-4">
      Gracias por visitar mi portfolio. Si tienes alguna pregunta o deseas
      colaborar, no dudes en contactarme.
    </p>
    <form
      action="https://formspree.io/f/mwkadplg"
      method="POST"
      class="flex flex-col space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:flex-row md:space-x-4 items-center w-full max-w-xl"
    >
      <input
        type="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="Tu correo electrónico"
        required
        class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-white bg-gray-800 w-full md:w-64"
      />
      <textarea
        name="message"
        placeholder="Tu mensaje"
        rows="1"
        required
        class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-white bg-gray-800 w-full md:w-64 resize-none"
      ></textarea>

      <button
        type="submit"
        class="button-footer px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-white bg-gray-800 flex items-center space-x-2"
      >
        <svg
        class="icon-footer"
          data-testid="geist-icon"
          height="16"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          viewBox="0 0 16 16"
          width="16"
          style="color: currentcolor;"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            clip-rule="evenodd"
            d="M7.29289 1.39644C7.68342 1.00592 8.31658 1.00592 8.70711 1.39644L11.7803 4.46966L12.3107 4.99999L11.25 6.06065L10.7197 5.53032L8.75 3.56065V10.25V11H7.25V10.25V3.56065L5.28033 5.53032L4.75 6.06065L3.68934 4.99999L4.21967 4.46966L7.29289 1.39644ZM13.5 9.24999V13.5H2.5V9.24999V8.49999H1V9.24999V14C1 14.5523 1.44771 15 2 15H14C14.5523 15 15 14.5523 15 14V9.24999V8.49999H13.5V9.24999Z"
            fill="currentColor"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="text">Enviar</span>
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div class="text-sm text-zinc-200/90 text-center mt-4">
    © {currentYear}
    <a href="" class="hover:underline">Ceri</a>
  </div>
</footer>
